{
  "stem": "21582.3",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And his mission in life was loving children.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "His mission in love-- in life was to be a parent to orphans.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And he ran orphanages.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I loved him.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "My first love was through books.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "He wrote books about-- all my friends read them.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "I think every Polish child read them.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "In his books, the heroes were children, and they became kings, and it was like turning tables.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And the world was run by children.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And we-- usually, during the summer, we would go to the country.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And one year we went to the country to a camp, a children's camp.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And there was a counselor who told us about-- she was an orphan and she was raised in his orphanage.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "So when she talked about Dr.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "Korczak, she talked about her father.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And she said, oh-- and, you know, I remember, we were wondering how could he be a father?",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We came from families of one, two, three, four maybe.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But how could he be a father to so many children?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And she said, oh, he was.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I remember one example that really registered with me, and that was she said every time a child was sick or had a loose tooth, they always ran to Dr.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Korczak, because if Dr.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Korczak pulled the tooth, it absolutely didn't hurt.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So you can see the love that he imparted and the love that the children felt for him.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Well, during the war, Dr.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Korczak still stayed in the ghetto with the orphanage.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And he was trying to raise money.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I remember my sister and I helped by-- there were also little children's theaters.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And we performed in the little-- in the children's theaters, and the funds went to the orphanage, to Dr.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Korczak.",
      "word_count": 1
    }
  ],
